title: Volunteers Needed This Weekend
body: HisLight Ministries is looking for two more volunteers for this weekend's Soup Kitchen. To sign up please visit https://hislightministries.com

title: Susan Hawthorne Meal Needs
body: Susan is recovering well from her back surgery, but she needs assistance with meals. Anybody who is able to contribute to helping her out with dinner please visit http://mealsforsusan.org
